    <item>
      <title>据称中国监管机构将要求部分银行降低债券风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/china-regulator-said-to-ask-some-banks-to-shorten-bond-duration-lygovx7w</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国金融监管机构要求一些农村银行缩短其债券持有的平均期限，以在债务市场持续上涨的背景下保护银行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/china-regulator-said-to-ask-some-banks-to-shorten-bond-duration-lygovx7w</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
