      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/bank-of-korea-stands-pat-with-focus-moving-to-rate-cut-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行行长李昌镕试图根据短期政策调整的假设来控制市场走势，同时央行委员会延续了创纪录的利率维持不变。]]></description>
